name: CerebralSpinalFluidCSFAnalysis
title: Cerebral Spinal Fluid (CSF) Analysis
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains laboratory observable panel code(s) for Cerebral Spinal Fluid (CSF) Analysis.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients with a lab test performed on a source of Cerebral Spinal Fluid.),(Inclusion Criteria: Cerebral Spinal Fluid (CSF) analysis lab test, coded in LOINC, using panel codes and test codes (individual laboratory observations) associated with these panel code(s).),(Exclusion Criteria: Does not include any codes which do not represent Cerebral Spinal Fluid (CSF) analysis as defined in the inclusion criteria.)
